OL,3,CMan airlifted to hospital with serious
OL,4,Cinjuries after six-vehicle collision
OL,6,FPolice were called to a six-vehicle
OL,7,Fcollision on the A66, near to the
OL,8,FBrigham turnoff in West Cumbria, at
OL,9,F10.57am today (Monday July 13).
OL,11,FIt involved two coaches, one van and
OL,12,Fthree cars.
OL,14,FA man who had been driving one of the
OL,15,Fcoaches suffered serious injuries and
OL,16,Fwas taken by helicopter to Royal
OL,17,FPreston Hospital.
OL,19,FPolice are asking any witnesses, or
OL,20,Fanyone with dash-cam footage to get in
OL,21,Ftouch.
